<summary>元スレッド・記事本文</summary>
<p><img alt="sss" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="/rss/downloaded_images/b5c41e212c0308d7014bf3fe1f4b54eb.png"></p>
